---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Privacy Policy | Stratton Digital Systems"
    description="Privacy policy describing how information is collected and used."
    pageClass="page-legal"
>
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container" style="max-width: 70ch;">
            <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

            <p>
                Stratton Digital Systems respects your privacy. This policy
                explains how information is collected and used when you visit
                this website or submit a form.
            </p>

            <h2>Information we collect</h2>
            <p>
                We may collect information you voluntarily provide, including
                your name, business name, email address, phone number, website
                URL, and any details you submit through our contact form.
            </p>

            <h2>How information is used</h2>
            <p>
                Information you provide is used only to respond to inquiries,
                provide requested services, and communicate about your request.
                We do not sell or share your information with third parties for
                marketing purposes.
            </p>

            <h2>Third-party services</h2>
            <p>
                Form submissions are processed using Formspree. Formspree may
                temporarily store submitted data to deliver messages. Their
                handling of data is governed by their own privacy policy.
            </p>

            <h2>Cookies and analytics</h2>
            <p>
                This website does not knowingly use cookies for tracking or
                advertising purposes. Basic server logs may be collected for
                security and performance reasons.
            </p>

            <h2>Data retention</h2>
            <p>
                Information is retained only as long as necessary to respond to
                inquiries or fulfill business obligations.
            </p>

            <h2>Contact</h2>
            <p>
                If you have questions about this policy, you may contact us
                through the website.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
